      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. Could you make it sound a bit less \"template-y\"? Specifically, I want to add a sentence or two that acknowledges how much we enjoyed the conversation and that it was a really tight race between him and the other candidate. Just something to soften the blow so it feels a bit more personal/sincere without losing the professional tone.",
